		"body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Move `window.addEventListener('resize')` and `ipcRenderer.on('asynchronous-message')` from the constructor to `componentDidMount`\r\n- Store handler references in private class fields so they can be properly removed\r\n- Add `ipcRenderer.removeListener` calls in `componentWillUnmount` for both `asynchronous-message` and `appClose` channels\r\n\r\nFixes memory leaks and duplicate handler execution caused by listeners registered in the constructor with no cleanup.\r\n\r\n## Test plan\r\n- App opens and closes normally\r\n-  Window resize still updates layout\r\n-  Callback URLs still open correctly\r\n-  App close (with notes being saved) still works correctly\r\n",
